replies.msg:
o係 <code>/etc/mpd.conf</code> 裡面可以enable 2 HiRes streaming service, 不過我冇戶口冇得試<img src="/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif" class="hkgmoji" /><br />
<br />
<pre><code data-type=""># QOBUZ input plugin
input {
        enabled    &quot;no&quot;
        plugin     &quot;qobuz&quot;
#        app_id     &quot;ID&quot;
#        app_secret &quot;SECRET&quot;
#        username   &quot;USERNAME&quot;
#        password   &quot;PASSWORD&quot;
#        format_id  &quot;N&quot;
}

# TIDAL input plugin
input {
        enabled      &quot;no&quot;
        plugin       &quot;tidal&quot;
#        token        &quot;TOKEN&quot;
#        username     &quot;USERNAME&quot;
#        password     &quot;PASSWORD&quot;
#        audioquality &quot;Q&quot;
}
</code></pre><br />
<br />
應該改一改就得

